<item>
            <title>[LU-19427] sanity-pcc test_99b: invalidate_lock deadlock with mixed buffered and direct I/O workload</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19427</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Found out the root reason of the deadlock in sanity-pcc/test_99b:&lt;br/&gt;
A client holding a PW extent lock L1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
T1d - T8d: read direct I/O

Client (OSC):

use out all available RPC slots;

00000008:00000008:1.0:1758255488.304183:0:5556:0:(osc_request.c:3049:osc_build_rpc()) [0x200000405:0x9:0x0]: 1024 read pages, start 8192, end 9216, now 9r/0w/9d in flight

OST Server side:

Waiting on the server side locking;

Lock callback to revoke the conflict L1 granted to the client;

&amp;lt;=== Depend on the completion of T2.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
T2: Client side lock blocking AST &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; L1 (OSC):

osc_dlm_blocking_ast0()-&amp;gt;osc_lock_flush()-&amp;gt;osc_lock_discard_pages():

exclusive invalidate_lock() : waiting mapping invalidate_lock

&amp;lt;=== Waiting &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; T3 or T4.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

T3: Fast read

generic_file_read_iter

-- Acquire share invalidate_lock

-- Waiting &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; page (folio) lock:

-- fast read pgno: 3072

-- f99b.sanity-pcc: read ppos: 12582912, count: 1048576

&amp;lt;=== Waiting &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; T4.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
T4: Generic file buffered read:

ll_file_io_generic()) f99b.sanity-pcc: read ppos: 12582912, count: 1048576 - buffered read
-- Acquire share invalidate_lock
-- Acquire the page (folio) lock: pgno=3072

lov_io_submit() -&amp;gt; osc_io_submit()

HANG &amp;lt;------------- Acquire page lock: pgno=3072, waiting &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; RPC slots.

&amp;lt;==== Waiting &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; T1d-T8d
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The deadlock: T1d-T8d =&amp;gt; T2 =&amp;gt; T3 | T4 =&amp;gt; T1d-T8d&lt;/p&gt;</description>
